# 懵然不知

(pos:成語, 名詞)
<explanation>
yue:完全不知道，對事物毫無認識或了解（多用於形容突然遇到事或聽到消息時的反應）
eng:completely unaware, utterly clueless

<eg>
yue:我聽到公司裁員嘅消息，懵然不知該如何應對。 (ng5 ting1 do4 sang1 pin2 jai6 ng6 pin1 baat3, mang1 jyun4 wai1 gei1 ngoi6 ying4 dou3.)
eng:I was completely unaware of the company's layoff news and didn't know how to respond.

yue:佢對整個事件懵然不知，直到新聞報道。 (ng5 joi5 zung1 go1 jing4 kei5 mang1 jyun4 wai1, zik6 dou4 sin1 bao2 daao4.)
eng:He was clueless about the entire incident until it was reported in the news. [end of text]


